syms u v
R = 2; r = 1;
x(u,v) = (R + r*cos(v)) *cos(u);
y(u,v) = (R + r*cos(v)) *sin(u);
z(u,v) = r*sin(v);
fsurf(x, y, z, [0 2*pi 0 2*pi])
axis equal










